Your employment status

 

Grey box content changed to:

Because you've pleaded guilty to at least 1 charge you must now tell us about your employment status.

This will:

make sure your fine is based on your circumstances

help to speed up the processing of your case

 

From the 6 options displayed

Employed

Employed and also receiving benefits

Self-employed

Self-employed and also receiving benefits

Receiving out of work benefits

Other

 

the user selects their employment status and then selects continue which takes them to the finance screen for that selection
